span>」<br />\n<br />\n港豬已經接受左被強姦中出既命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實買樓果班從未冇嘈過鉛水，永遠係得公屋果班嘈，咁你就明白香港人為左層樓，屎水都照飲都冇問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕樓價下降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00ffa9da190086b953a7d5c6314b4ca63269f51","tid":339391,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fde2efb349a65fc9f56ee4ae80331d711b2054a","tid":339391,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f20876aab3e893794f01b202f07e09dcf5440db","tid":339391,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:43:24.000Z","msg":"中國建築啲料好呢hea<br />\n成日聽到公司啲啊頭呻下"},{"pid":"c84eac2a018d074d8f027baa1fc97800540e48e4","tid":339391,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:50:35.000Z","msg":"投多d比保皇狗啦"},{"pid":"c369a53591c6336ec1d6883d493f444e52532913","tid":339391,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實鉛水呢招 <br />\n係美國已經用到爛<br />\n雲姨姨有無新招呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用到爛<br />\n咁解決左未啊！<br />\n支那狗<br />\n你呢招五毛都用到爛啦"},{"pid":"b0222418aa60a975e9f44ffb2152f4d216354563","tid":339391,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d3ea120767f2f4d2c22a104015993b2128d1587","tid":339391,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8ae38e5242464ba7f902a684b6c8fde859a5bae","tid":339391,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"