到爛啦</blockquote><br />\n民主派打手出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n駁唔到啊你？<br />\n支那狗"},{"pid":"bf82a6b2f834518a199a03dcf808adc466b2face","tid":339391,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申明眼港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬你老母<br />\n支那狗就支那狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8784b41a946f7f8fff4ffade3e72cc43ed7d1b27","tid":339391,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2413556ecfa3d33fbd58189dbe862bf334760dd3","tid":339391,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:39:23.000Z","msg":"大家都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71058c92048eb6319d2d1312b7f037b9b7937fe4","tid":339391,"uid":85284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:53:07.000Z","msg":"經過喺某強國過去咁多年嘅實踐同經驗<br />\n各種慢性毒／殺害人民嘅方法同手段佢哋已經嫻熟手巧<br />\n只不過大部份人嘅思維係喺冇即時嚴重嘅身體反應<br />\n咁就會覺得沒有問題<br />\n例如俾人長期喺飲食甚至冷氣／空氣長期落藥（唔係污染物）<br />\n導致身體發熱，燃燒身體體內之物<br />\n身體痕癢<br />\n尿頻<br />\n興奮狀態<br />\n長期惡劣睡眠質素<br />\n甚至長期失眠眼光光  等等<br />\n<br />\n如果係因為被落藥所得嘅表面癥狀去求醫<br />\n你會死得仲快<br />\n<br />\n好多人其實自己身處戰場被單方面慢性屠殺<br />\n仲係懵然不知"},{"pid":"65cd8a84150466b1aa5db93b25a98b4c3a171e82","tid":339391,"uid":124323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:59:58.000Z","msg":"中國良好教育-飲水思鉛"},{"pid":"1a32a7c88ad8fdcb9139c1e6415487291d22b30e","tid":339391,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實鉛水呢招 <br />\n係美國已經用到爛<br />\n雲姨姨有無新招呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用到爛<br />\n咁解決左未啊！<br />\n支那狗<br />\n你呢招五毛都用到爛